      description "Additional definitions from MOM:min/max-elements:0/32; Data radio bearer user plane profile. Instances DrbUp=Default_application_signaling, Default_conversational_media, and Default_other are created automatically when parent MO instance is created, unless created manually in same transaction. DU5qi::drbUpRef is automatically set to following MO instance: - DrbUp=Default_application_signaling instance for DU5qi instances for which profile5qi is 5 or 69. - DrbUp=Default_conversational_media instance for DU5qi instances for which profile5qi is 1, 65, or 66. - DrbUp=Default_other instance for all other DU5qi instances. Unless manually set to refer to another MO instance. DrbUp=Default_application_signaling, Default_conversational_media, and Default_other instances are used for DRBs when DU5qi instance with matching profile5qi does not exist. Only applicable when GNBDUFunction::altDepHServAdapUPProfEnabled is true. Precondition: Instances DrbUp=Default_application_signaling, Default_conversational_media, and Default_other can only be created in same transaction as parent MO instance and cannot be deleted unless parent MO instance is deleted. Other instances can be created and deleted at any time. Maximum 29 DrbUp instances, with RDN different from Default_application_signaling, Default_conversational_media, and Default_other, can be created under parent MO instance.";
      key "drbUpId";
      leaf drbUpId {
        type leafref {
