      description "Aggregated time for downlink MAC latency measurement for each QoS without DRX impact and out-of-sync impact. DL MAC latency measures MAC scheduling latency between reception of packet in an empty DL buffer and transmission of first packet. Unit: 125 microseconds Compressed: True.";
