      description "Number of resource block symbols used for PDSCH for codebook and reciprocity beamforming. DMRS and PTRS embedded in PDSCH resources are included. Unit: N/A Ranges: Bin[0]: UE configured with SRS and PDSCH is reciprocity-based Bin[1]: UE configured with SRS and PDSCH is codebook-based Bin[2]: UE not configured with SRS and PDSCH is codebook-based Bin[3]: UE configured with SRS and PDSCH is configured with common beamforming weights.";
      type ietfyang:mac-address;
