      description "Measured noise and interference power on PUSCH. Unit: N/A Ranges: Bin[0]: [..-130] dBm/PRB Bin[1]: ]-130..-128] dBm/PRB Bin[2]: ]-128..-126] dBm/PRB Bin[3]: ]-126..-124] dBm/PRB Bin[4]: ]-124..-122] dBm/PRB Bin[5]: ]-122..-121] dBm/PRB Bin[6]: ]-121..-120] dBm/PRB Bin[7]: ]-120..-119] dBm/PRB Bin[8]: ]-119..-118] dBm/PRB Bin[9]: ]-118..-117] dBm/PRB Bin[10]: ]-117..-116] dBm/PRB Bin[11]: ]-116..-115] dBm/PRB Bin[12]: ]-115..-114] dBm/PRB Bin[13]: ]-114..-113] dBm/PRB Bin[14]: ]-113..-112] dBm/PRB Bin[15]: ]-112..-108] dBm/PRB Bin[16]: ]-108..-104] dBm/PRB Bin[17]: ]-104..-100] dBm/PRB Bin[18]: ]-100..-96] dBm/PRB Bin[19]: ]-96..-92] dBm/PRB Bin[20]: ]-92..] dBm/PRB.";
