18]: Total number of successful initial downlink HARQ transmissions using 16-QAM on slot 18. Bin[19]: Total number of successful initial downlink HARQ transmissions using 16-QAM on slot 19..";
      type ietfyang:mac-address;
      max-elements 20;
    }
    leaf-list pmRadioMacShortPsrRsrpDistr {
      description "Distribution of last measured widebeam RSRP values at time of decision to switch scheduling request on PUCCH periodicity to shorter periodicity. Ranges: Bin[0]: [..-116] dBm Bin[1]: ]-116..-114] dBm Bin[2]: ]-114..-112] dBm Bin[3]: ]-112..-110] dBm Bin[4]: ]-110..-108] dBm Bin[5]: ]-108..-106] dBm Bin[6]: ]-106..-104] dBm Bin[7]: ]-104..-102] dBm Bin[8]: ]-102..-100] dBm Bin[9]: ]-100..-98] dBm Bin[10]: ]-98..-96] dBm Bin[11]: ]-96..-94] dBm Bin[12]: ]-94..-92] dBm Bin[13]: ]-92..-90] dBm Bin[14]: ]-90..] dBm Unit: N/A.";
      type ietfyang:mac-address;
      max-elements 15;
    }
    leaf-list pmMacRBSymUsedPdschAdvSuMimoLayerDistr {
