PUSCH scheduled entities in uplink slot. Bin[33]: 33 PUSCH scheduled entities in uplink slot. Bin[34]: 34 PUSCH scheduled entities in uplink slot. Bin[35]: 35 PUSCH scheduled entities in uplink slot. Bin[36]: 36 PUSCH scheduled entities in uplink slot..";
