      description "Distribution of precoding weights reported by UE for rank 1 codebook associated with secondary CSI-RS. Indicates spatial distribution of UEs using cell as PCell. Type 1 single-panel codebooks are defined in 3GPP TS 38.214. Represents distribution of requested departure angles from AAS-capable radio unit as estimated from UE CSI feedback, specifically main and diversity direction of PMI values. It is not recommended to use this PM counter for Remote radio units. For more information, see Massive MIMO Mid-Band and Manage Massive MIMO NR in CPI library. Unit: N/A Compressed: True.";
