      description "Estimated average power distribution over time relative to maximum TX power in each control step for SectorCarrier for direction 6. Unit: N/A Ranges: Bin[0]: [0..2.5] % Bin[1]: ]2.5..5] % Bin[2]: ]5..7.5] % Bin[3]: ]7.5..10] % Bin[4]: ]10..12.5] % Bin[5]: ]12.5..15] % Bin[6]: ]15..17.5] % Bin[7]: ]17.5..20] % Bin[8]: ]20..22.5] % Bin[9]: ]22.5..25] % Bin[10]: ]25..27.5] % Bin[11]: ]27.5..30] % Bin[12]: ]30..32.5] % Bin[13]: ]32.5..35] % Bin[14]: ]35..37.5] % Bin[15]: ]37.5..40] % Bin[16]: ]40..42.5] % Bin[17]: ]42.5..45] % Bin[18]: ]45..47.5] % Bin[19]: ]47.5..50] % Bin[20]: ]50..52.5] % Bin[21]: ]52.5..55] % Bin[22]: ]55..57.5] % Bin[23]: ]57.5..60] % Bin[24]: ]60..62.5] % Bin[25]: ]62.5..65] % Bin[26]: ]65..67.5] % Bin[27]: ]67.5..70] % Bin[28]: ]70..72.5] % Bin[29]: ]72.5..75] % Bin[30]: ]75..77.5] % Bin[31]: ]77.5..80] % Bin[32]: ]80..82.5] % Bin[33]: ]82.5..85] % Bin[34]: ]85..87.5] % Bin[35]: ]87.5..90] % Bin[36]: ]90..92.5] % Bin[37]: ]92.5..95] % Bin[38]: ]95..97.5] % Bin[39]: ]97.5..100] %.";
